{"tid":930211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【1個都不能少】不只范冰冰們！中國打逃稅瞄準百姓　欠稅10萬人民幣禁出國","createTime":"2018-12-06T06:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T13:08:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9fdafa1c4c39df00aee25e7a8d0d16c343e9f0","tid":930211,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181206/640_71e0d0f720c81d4e574512531849b128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181206%2F640_71e0d0f720c81d4e574512531849b128.jpg&h=9c60e900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彭博引述新華社報導指出，中國打擊逃稅的力道越來越重，對象已不限富賈巨商或影視歌星，而是向下延伸到老百姓，欠稅太多的人將禁止離開中國。<br />\n報導內容說，根據中國稅務總局上個月頒布的新規定，未繳清稅款超過10萬人民幣（約45.5萬台幣）者，就會被禁止出國旅遊，門檻從舊規的超過100萬人民幣大幅下調。<br />\n新規定於明年元旦生效。<br />\n中國對逃稅施壓越來越重，包括今年稍早採取的一系列高調行動，許多隱匿財富的名人不但被曝光還遭重罰。<br />\n今年10月，中國命令影視一姐范冰冰與所屬公司，補稅及罰款超過8億人民幣，折合新台幣近40億元。<br />\n范冰冰今年稍早一度失聯，10月才重新出現，透過微博為逃稅道歉，並承諾支付鉅額補稅及罰款。<br />\n除了嚴打逃稅，中國也將在明年元旦執行新的個人稅制，放寬較低收入的等級，並要求外國人與持有海外資產的中國人多繳稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181206/1478644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181206%2F1478644&d=OnQhE1jfOhsITLw1mWoZi8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d99797d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181206%2F1478644&h=516709fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181206/1478644</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-12-05/not-just-fan-bingbing-china-steps-up-crackdown-on-tax-evaders\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2018-12-05%2Fnot-just-fan-bingbing-china-steps-up-crackdown-on-tax-evaders&d=OnQhE1jfOhsITLw1mWoZi8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=acdedb70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-12-05/not-just-fan-bingbing-china-steps-up-crackdown-on-tax-evaders</a>"},{"pid":"45aa6d85c09ff2c4cde771907fe12d486e762088","tid":930211,"uid":18912,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"中史<br />\n苛捐雜税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n橫征暴斂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd41600f9d28523fd11d573a341730caac940c0","tid":930211,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:59:56.000Z","msg":"即係所有人"},{"pid":"9a7693bf398c1af488fbd0b0089f3531e623013a","tid":930211,"uid":61300,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"45aa6d85c09ff2c4cde771907fe12d486e762088","tid":930211,"uid":18912,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"中史<br />\n苛捐雜税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n橫征暴斂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"亡國先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6052c3cc721e94cbd8bd8072d157f010873b4686","tid":930211,"uid":59192,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"45aa6d85c09ff2c4cde771907fe12d486e762088","tid":930211,"uid":18912,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"中史<br />\n苛捐雜税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n橫征暴斂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"依家只不過係追番人地欠左既稅<br />\n點睇都好合理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f7079f8a54090d4e189379259444dbec641235","tid":930211,"uid":12208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6052c3cc721e94cbd8bd8072d157f010873b4686","tid":930211,"uid":59192,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"